<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.3">
<l>ammait taṭaṅkaṇ maṭavāyc ciyaru</l>
<l rend="indent">māṉā yarumā niraiyum alaṟi</l>
<l>yemmaic caraṇēṉ ṟukoḷḷeṉ ṟirappa</l>
<l rend="indent">vilaṅkā ḻikkaiyen taiyeṭut tamalai</l>
<l>tammaic caraṇeṉ ṟatampā vaiyaraip</l>
<l rend="indent">puṉamēy kiṉṟamā ṉiṉaṅkāṇ miṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>kommaip puyakkuṉ ṟarcilai kuṉikkum</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉuṅkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain that our father lifted, with the shining discus in hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">when, weeping, the simple herdesses</l>
<l rend="indent">with wide, beautiful, kohl [lined] eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">cow-herders, and herds of cows begged,</l>
<l rend="indent">“please accept our request for refuge,”</l>
<l>called Govardana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where big shouldered mountain men bend their bows,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying,“look [at] the deer herd grazing in the uplands,”</l>
<l rend="indent">to ladies who [then] say to them, “[give] them refuge”</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
